{{version030}}
{{Flavour|Summons wandering mushrooms and deathcaps next to a targeted creature.}}

'''Summon Mushrooms''' is a monster-only spell which summons several [[wandering mushroom]]s and [[deathcap]]s, surrounding the target. The mushrooms themselves are unlikely to be a major threat by the time you reach [[Zot]], but they can get in the way of movement, [[confuse]] you, and finish off players who have been [[torment]]ed too many times.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Prior to [[0.13]], Summon Mushrooms only summoned wandering mushrooms.

[[Category:Monster spells]]
